Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.40,Flashback,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:12.59,Flashback,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, it's Fukami, from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.33,Flashback,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.78,Flashback,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Okikura-kun, hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.66,Flashback,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:23.66,Flashback-Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see the future, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.22,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That thing just now—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:02.47,Episode-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(483,474)}Episode 3\N"Utility Tank"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:00.97,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, is that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:03.10,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:05.14,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet up to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.98,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.29,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:10.44,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get late if we meet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:14.21,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.94,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to finish up some things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.04,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I have a really important guest—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:40.05,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Piece! Yeah, piece—that I'm going to work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.04,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So don't come into the workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:46.09,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but be done by dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.09,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.50,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hard worker, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.83,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Yana-chan that Yuki-kun liked...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.45,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,And Okikura-kun is coming over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.96,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.83,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-kun and Yana-chan are\N such precious friends to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.61,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,They always have been, \Nand they always will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:40.10,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But even if my feelings don't change,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.99,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,our friendships might.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.88,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:33.29,glassware,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Try glassware\Nsingle-flower cups
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.42,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make Yana-chan cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.43,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.58,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.68,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:50.81,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:59.63,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,This is why glass is your medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.33,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:04.90,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,A guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.09,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.24,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,We're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.46,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for taking care of my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:11.55,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring tea—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.41,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Okikura-kun was just about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.50,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell Mom and Dad, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.72,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,We're having pork cutlets tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:24.84,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:31.45,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you came only to \Nhave me kick you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.47,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:37.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see Yana-chan \Nand Yuki-kun's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.48,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yukinari Imi confess \Nto you or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.94,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.38,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan realized there was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:50.57,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,someone Yuki-kun liked,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.63,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,so she came to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:56.51,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been the only \None who hadn't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:01.76,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What would you have done, \Nhaving seen their future?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:05.55,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to think of a way to make \Nsure we wouldn't get torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.87,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that can be granted,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:11.24,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,but I like that you put \Neffort into everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.92,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine from here. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.62,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the mountain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.81,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.32,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.47,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking maybe you haven't made
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.99,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,many new friends here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.29,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I make a point to go hiking by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.07,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.94,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one who didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:43.96,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.16,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have trouble sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:11.61,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,A bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:13.81,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I need another way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.81,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:17.24,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's important for girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:21.06,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you need to bring \Na dryer on a hiking trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.42,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What if my hair gets messed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.57,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we even going \Nto find wall sockets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:28.26,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rechargeable, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:31.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:32.54,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:32.79,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.09,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.06,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.81,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.67,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.57,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Nee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.59,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:54.62,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I took the wrong road. Tee hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:00.76,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're really, really going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.72,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:05.00,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me. I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Call me right away if you get worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.97,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,See you at the meet-up spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Back up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:29.24,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you a few times before, Sacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.84,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Can I call you "Sacchan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:32.82,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.84,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around here goes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.44,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,to the central hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.47,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:41.87,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a cute pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.12,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.98,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,It was a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.58,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:50.23,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,From who, your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.97,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, but it's someone I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:55.47,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, he's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.35,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.27,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.36,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,my kid brother's out-of-touch \Nwhen it comes to girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.72,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,and he worries about silly \Nthings like his height,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.71,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,but he's a good guy at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:12.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.11,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Be good to him, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.26,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:33.13,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Were you too pumped about today to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.80,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura-kun came over yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura-kun is that new student, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed like he'd like mountains. \NMaybe we should have invited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:47.06,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but he said he likes hiking alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,A lone wolf, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.25,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I like hiking with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:55.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, another half-hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.72,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.41,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:22.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.18,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, it was fun in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.70,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been on one,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.48,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,but I imagine it's what roller coasters are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.69,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Roller...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.32,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll come pick you up when it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.95,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.35,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You be careful, too—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.91,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's like the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.20,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Living with her, she's more like a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.26,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.15,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Look, mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.84,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,And the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.79,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,We just came up a mountain, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.07,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It feels awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's still snow over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.87,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Hinode Mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.38,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get some water in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:40.76,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.95,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Where can we go for water, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.54,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:46.90,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't, Sachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:50.20,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're probably the weakest one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.54,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:53.71,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're in charge of the tents, Yukinari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.40,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.50,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.72,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine if we look all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.58,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,and it turns out there's water right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.34,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Yana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.77,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I wanted \Nto ask you, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.75,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh hey, a creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.09,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.74,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to go out with Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:46.80,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.67,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:50.62,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.65,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:08.40,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I set up sheets. You can sit down and read.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.79,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.77,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.75,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.35,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they couldn't figure \Nout where to get water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's a tap just over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty thoughtful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like yakisoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.59,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,With a lot of pickled red ginger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.18,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,We should be okay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.43,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're so bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.82,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.73,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.82,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just have bad timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:12.46,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:19.30,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, what did you think about Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.46,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.59,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:26.64,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:29.60,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't normally say "thanks" \Nafter being confessed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.55,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.22,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.23,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.52,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.05,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, are you going to go out with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.15,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.62,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-kun's really cool
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:51.97,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,but my romance sensor didn't go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.03,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Your what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.98,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you have such a thing installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.04,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad I can't show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.33,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.31,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be a bit more obvious if
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:12.47,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,you liked him, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.57,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I decided to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.15,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:20.90,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.36,Sign,Text,0000,0000,0000,,No service
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.86,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't get lost here \Neven if you tried, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.33,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:47.65,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you the one screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.34,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.55,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,And damn yourself to an \Neternity of fetching water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're so beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:08.54,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,the way you're so invested in reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.42,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're like
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:13.70,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,a doll to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:16.74,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty. A poem or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.99,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where're the noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:22.89,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:24.71,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.47,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:29.45,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.93,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.27,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:34.27,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back. What's the water for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.85,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,For Hiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.43,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do I dump it on his head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,How about I dump it on {\i1}your{\0} head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:43.39,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that freaked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.69,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:50.85,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.14,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,A token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.13,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:56.66,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.07,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Token.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:06.63,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.47,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some if it gets \Non the menu. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:10.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.64,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.99,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You were like a doll to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:31.75,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.12,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:43.50,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,How's your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:47.42,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's not burnt or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.46,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.01,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,For taking care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:04.22,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, thanks to you, t—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.48,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,You can read it now, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.71,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, I,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.59,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,well—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.81,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I—Sachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:17.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I like your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.48,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:57.78,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's someone \Nthat's more suited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.28,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:02.04,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:04.12,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.05,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:08.29,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.21,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:14.51,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.77,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to be such a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.06,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.62,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:36.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:39.54,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I saw a boar on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.32,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,It looked pretty vicious, \Nso if you run into one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.48,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,don't pretend to be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that for bears?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.48,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:48.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.12,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I didn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.58,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't take long to pack up, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.42,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,We're done, Nee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:59.21,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting a ride home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.00,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.47,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Café next time, then, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.09,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything today, Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.14,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.03,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Nee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:16.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.86,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, are you doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:25.54,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go, before we run into boars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:28.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there are more \Naccidents going down mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.92,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay, whatever, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.92,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,than going up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.99,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.88,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.70,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.05,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:40.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:41.97,Main,Yuiki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:21:01.44,bridge,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinode \NBridge
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.20,Sign,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan\N{\fs14}Text Message
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:09.79,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,To Touko-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:12.23,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.76,Italics,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:14.68,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:15.66,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.49,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hina-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:26.06,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,what would you do if your best friend \Ngot confessed to by someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:27.65,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,You got confessed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.85,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:34.44,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:36.63,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:39.54,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It'd depend on whether I liked \Nthe person back or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What else could I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.19,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.53,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:51.60,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,So that guy from the other day—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.85,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,did he go hiking with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.13,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, he didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.47,Main,Off-screen,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru is a weird name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.36,Main,Off-screen,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi—nice name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:33.76,Main,Off-screen,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of awesome, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:34.88,Main,Off-screen,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.35,Main,Off-screen,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:38.14,Episode-Title - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4:\N"Steep Road"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:38.14,Main,Off-screen,0000,0000,0000,,You're showing off a bit, aren't you?
